channel.title: Small little bug [Fixed]
channel.description:
At the very beginning when the torso falls on you out of ventilation pipe. You can put a box under the pipe. Then you put the barrel on top of the box and get into the pipe. Inside there is a hole in the world that shows as a white portal to oblivion.
This is a small bug, but still looks unclean.
